Source: darkstat
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: CloudArmour Packaging Team <opensource@cloudarmour.io>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), autoconf, automake, libpcap-dev, zlib1g-dev
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Rules-Requires-Root: binary-targets
Homepage: https://unix4lyfe.org/darkstat/

Package: darkstat
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: lightweight real-time network traffic monitor with web UI
 darkstat sniffs packets on a chosen network interface, accumulates traffic
 statistics (hosts, ports, protocols, graphs), and serves them over HTTP.
 .
 This packaging branch includes JSON export support at /json to simplify
 integrations with monitoring and automation systems.
